And despite the warnings.

260
00:12:04.098 --> 00:12:07.936
I still have my sight
set on finding a curse.

261
00:12:07.977 --> 00:12:10.605
So I'm heading to a city famous

262
00:12:10.647 --> 00:12:12.774
for its history of voodoo.

263
00:12:12.815 --> 00:12:16.069
{\an8}(tense dramatic music)

264
00:12:19.822 --> 00:12:22.742
Celebrated for its festivals and nightlife.

265
00:12:22.784 --> 00:12:25.203
New Orleans is just as well known

266
00:12:25.244 --> 00:12:28.081
for its long association with magic.

267
00:12:28.957 --> 00:12:31.626
And I'm hoping I've come to the right place

268
00:12:31.668 --> 00:12:33.878
in search of a curse.

269
00:12:34.796 --> 00:12:37.382
But it's hard to separate
the myths of voodoo

270
00:12:37.423 --> 00:12:40.093
from its authentic practice.

271
00:12:40.134 --> 00:12:42.637
So first. I'm seeking out an expert

272
00:12:42.679 --> 00:12:45.765
to find out just what is voodoo.

273
00:12:45.807 --> 00:12:47.058
- That's the question. right?

274
00:12:47.100 --> 00:12:49.060
What is voodoo mean? (laughs)

275
00:12:49.102 --> 00:12:52.355
{\an8}And some people say it
means spirit or divinity.

276
00:12:52.397 --> 00:12:56.234
{\an8}deity. you know. we
have a concept called ashe.

277
00:12:56.276 --> 00:12:58.486
{\an8}which is the divine.
sacred energy of things.

278
00:12:58.528 --> 00:13:01.364
Everything has ashe. this chair has ashe.

279
00:13:01.406 --> 00:13:03.616
the crossroads has a space. has ashe.

280
00:13:03.866 --> 00:13:05.827
and we celebrate the ashe in ourselves.

281
00:13:05.868 --> 00:13:09.414
and also outside in the
wild world where we find it.

282
00:13:09.455 --> 00:13:11.249
To me. that's what voodoo really is.

283
00:13:11.291 --> 00:13:13.001
It's sort of an understanding

284
00:13:13.042 --> 00:13:14.752
that everything is interconnected.

285
00:13:16.754 --> 00:13:20.216
There's so many misconceptions
about voodoo that it's.

286
00:13:20.258 --> 00:13:21.843
I mean. I think people hopefully

287
00:13:21.884 --> 00:13:23.928
are coming to terms things like. you know.

288
00:13:23.970 --> 00:13:25.221
that it's not all negative.

289
00:13:25.263 --> 00:13:26.556
that it's bad. that it's dark.

290
00:13:26.597 --> 00:13:27.849
I think people understand

291
00:13:27.890 --> 00:13:29.976
that like voodoo dolls
aren't really a thing.

292
00:13:30.018 --> 00:13:33.104
they understand that
zombies aren't really a thing.

293
00:13:33.146 --> 00:13:35.440
On the other hand. it also does have things

294
00:13:35.481 --> 00:13:39.569
that are very centered on curses and hexes

295
00:13:39.610 --> 00:13:42.697
and what people would
think of as negative magic.

296
00:13:42.739 --> 00:13:44.407
But what I say to people is.

297
00:13:44.449 --> 00:13:47.869
if you knew your partner or
your child was getting hurt.

298
00:13:47.910 --> 00:13:49.078
would you retaliate.

299
00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:51.080
would you just sit there and do nothing?

300
00:13:51.122 --> 00:13:53.374
You know. you're gonna try and resist

301
00:13:53.416 --> 00:13:55.168
and stop them from getting hurt

302
00:13:55.209 --> 00:13:57.128
with whatever you have at your disposal.

303
00:13:57.170 --> 00:13:59.088
And we have this very powerful magic.

304
00:13:59.130 --> 00:14:04.135
(birds chittering) (gentle dramatic music)

305
00:14:07.722 --> 00:14:10.099
- [Liam] Witchcraft. like all religions.

306
00:14:10.141 --> 00:14:14.020
is complex. and oftentimes contradictory.

307
00:14:14.062 --> 00:14:17.690
And I now know curses are
practiced in this tradition.

308
00:14:18.775 --> 00:14:20.026
So I've reached out

309
00:14:20.068 --> 00:14:21.986
to a well-known voodoo priest

310
00:14:22.028 --> 00:14:24.405
in the hope that they might be receptive

311
00:14:24.447 --> 00:14:27.325
to my search for dark magic.

312
00:14:29.660 --> 00:14:32.038
- Greetings. welcome.
- Thank you.

313
00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:33.956
- Wash your hands for me and come on in.

314
00:14:34.457 --> 00:14:36.209
- Okay. absolutely.

315
00:14:36.250 --> 00:14:38.586
- It's a bit of a blessing.
- Thank you.

316
00:14:38.628 --> 00:14:41.172
- And a slick way to get
some sanitizer on you.

317
00:14:41.214 --> 00:14:43.841
And welcome to the
House of the Divine Prince.

318
00:14:43.883 --> 00:14:44.801
{\an8}- Thank you so much.

319
00:14:45.093 --> 00:14:46.969
{\an8}- This is my sacred space.

320
00:14:47.011 --> 00:14:49.764
{\an8}This is my ministry room. if you will.

321
00:14:49.806 --> 00:14:51.432
{\an8}You see Santeria in this room.

322
00:14:51.474 --> 00:14:53.392
you see Lucumi in this room.

323
00:14:53.434 --> 00:14:54.852
you see Ifa in this room.

324
00:14:54.894 --> 00:14:58.272
and certainly you see
Voodoo present in this room.

325
00:14:58.314 --> 00:15:00.900
- One piece that I've noticed
is this piece down here.

326
00:15:00.983 --> 00:15:02.026
Could you tell me a little bit about that?

327
00:15:02.068 --> 00:15:03.945
- You need to be careful with that.

328
00:15:03.986 --> 00:15:05.738
Stand up.
- Okay.

329
00:15:05.780 --> 00:15:06.989
- This is a spirit double.

330
00:15:07.031 --> 00:15:09.367
it's a warrior. if you will.

331
00:15:09.408 --> 00:15:11.411
So he handles all the bad things

332
00:15:11.452 --> 00:15:14.080
that I can't do in the spirit realm.

333
00:15:14.122 --> 00:15:18.000
And each of those nails
represent a successful mission

334
00:15:18.042 --> 00:15:20.294
for which this deity has operated.

335
00:15:20.336 --> 00:15:24.799
This piece has done some
powerful things for me.

336
00:15:24.841 --> 00:15:27.051
And so I keep people away from it.

337
00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:31.180
- So can you tell me the sorts of things

338
00:15:31.222 --> 00:15:33.933
that people come to you looking for?

339
00:15:33.975 --> 00:15:35.476
- They look to be blessed.

340
00:15:35.518 --> 00:15:36.936
they look to be cleansed.

341
00:15:36.978 --> 00:15:39.105
they look to be protected.

342
00:15:39.147 --> 00:15:40.773
I channel the ancestors.

343
00:15:40.815 --> 00:15:44.318
I channel loa. orisha deities.

344
00:15:44.360 --> 00:15:47.947
and certainly I need the head of the client

345
00:15:47.989 --> 00:15:51.701
to be active in the ritual.

346
00:15:51.742 --> 00:15:54.495
So I can't do something to you. you know.

347
00:15:54.537 --> 00:15:57.456
that you're not willing to accept.

348
00:15:57.498 --> 00:16:00.501
- This might sound an unusual request.

349
00:16:00.543 --> 00:16:03.796
but I'm interested in finding a curse.

350
00:16:03.838 --> 00:16:05.715
a hex in some way.

351
00:16:05.756 --> 00:16:09.469
Not to visually prove anything on camera.

352
00:16:09.510 --> 00:16:11.679
but personally prove to myself

353
00:16:11.721 --> 00:16:13.556
that I can experience something.

354
00:16:13.598 --> 00:16:15.308
- Makes no sense to me at all.

355
00:16:16.684 --> 00:16:20.980
You're looking for a
curse to validate what?

356
00:16:21.022 --> 00:16:24.984
And so a positive thing. a blessing.

357
00:16:25.943 --> 00:16:28.237
a miraculous thing won't do that for you.

358
00:16:28.279 --> 00:16:29.614
it has to be a curse.

359
00:16:29.655 --> 00:16:32.742
- A positive thing feels like
it could just be something

360
00:16:32.783 --> 00:16:34.076
that happens on day to day.

361
00:16:34.118 --> 00:16:35.578
whereas something more like a curse

362
00:16:35.620 --> 00:16:38.206
might be more out of the unusual

363
00:16:38.247 --> 00:16:40.666
and something that would validate

364
00:16:40.708 --> 00:16:42.251
for my own personal belief.

365
00:16:42.293 --> 00:16:43.419
- As a Black man in America.

366
00:16:43.461 --> 00:16:45.671
I feel the exact opposite.

367
00:16:47.215 --> 00:16:49.008
I deal with the curse every day.

368
00:16:49.050 --> 00:16:51.385
I go through hell every day.

369
00:16:51.427 --> 00:16:53.679
People are calling me
and contacting me for help.

370
00:16:53.721 --> 00:16:57.433
who are cursed every day.

371
00:16:57.475 --> 00:16:59.477
The norm is to be cursed.

372
00:16:59.518 --> 00:17:04.482
And so it sounds.
without being disrespectful.

373
00:17:04.523 --> 00:17:06.483
almost entitled.

374
00:17:06.526 --> 00:17:07.359
- That's a good point.

375
00:17:07.401 --> 00:17:09.654
and I don't mean to
make light of it at all.

376
00:17:09.694 --> 00:17:13.782
I feel like I'm looking for something harsh

377
00:17:13.824 --> 00:17:16.993
so that it can grab my attention

378
00:17:17.036 --> 00:17:20.122
and give me some
understanding of what it is

379
00:17:20.164 --> 00:17:22.916
that may be beyond
this materialistic world.

380
00:17:23.834 --> 00:17:26.546
- I can't tell you how dangerous that is.

381
00:17:28.589 --> 00:17:31.509
And what you're opening yourself up to.

382
00:17:31.550 --> 00:17:33.553
losing everything.

383
00:17:33.594 --> 00:17:37.848
Oh. I'm about to sound
like an evangelical Christian.

384
00:17:37.890 --> 00:17:40.393
You're literally begging the Devil

385
00:17:40.434 --> 00:17:41.560
to knock on your door.

386
00:17:41.602 --> 00:17:43.771
just to prove to you that God's real.

387
00:17:44.730 --> 00:17:48.150
There are rules to our universe.

388
00:17:48.192 --> 00:17:49.944
And even before it comes outta our mouth.

389
00:17:49.986 --> 00:17:53.739
it's gotta be in our consciousness.

390
00:17:53.781 --> 00:17:57.660
So the universe has
already heard your request.

391
00:17:57.702 --> 00:17:59.620
- The position that you see the world from

392
00:17:59.662 --> 00:18:02.415
is not something that's very
easy for me to be able to see.

393
00:18:02.456 --> 00:18:04.709
We need to experience things for ourselves.

394
00:18:04.750 --> 00:18:06.794
and that's what I'm doing.

395
00:18:06.836 --> 00:18:09.005
I'm looking for a personal experience.

396
00:18:09.046 --> 00:18:10.214
- My fear at this point

397
00:18:10.256 --> 00:18:15.261
is that the wheels are in motion

398
00:18:15.428 --> 00:18:17.430
because it doesn't matter what you tell me.

399
00:18:17.471 --> 00:18:20.057
you've already released that.

400
00:18:20.099 --> 00:18:24.687
and I can only accept
that you absolutely believe

401
00:18:24.729 --> 00:18:27.106
what you're saying. scares me.

402
00:18:29.275 --> 00:18:31.027
A curse could end your life.

403
00:18:31.068 --> 00:18:32.486
then what are you proving?

404
00:18:33.738 --> 00:18:35.197
I'm dead now. but wow.

405
00:18:35.239 --> 00:18:38.075
now I know that there's
something really beyond this.

406
00:18:39.827 --> 00:18:43.831
Ooh. y'all better not call me

407
00:18:43.873 --> 00:18:45.124
at two o'clock in the morning

408
00:18:45.166 --> 00:18:46.792
talking about this man is dead.

409
00:18:46.834 --> 00:18:48.669
I. I don't want to hear that.

410
00:18:50.421 --> 00:18:51.756
I don't want to hear that.

411
00:18:51.797 --> 00:18:55.051
(eerie dramatic music)

412
00:19:03.643 --> 00:19:07.730
(eerie dramatic music continues)

413
00:19:20.034 --> 00:19:21.410
- [Ali] Hey. how are you doing?

414
00:19:21.452 --> 00:19:22.286
- Hi. Ali.

415
00:19:22.662 --> 00:19:26.665
We've been having a tough little
bit of a tough time out here.

416
00:19:26.707 --> 00:19:30.670
I'm struggling to convince anyone

417
00:19:30.711 --> 00:19:35.716
of my. of my meaning and my intention.

418
00:19:36.050 --> 00:19:38.177
- [Ali] What's happening
when you talk to them?

419
00:19:38.219 --> 00:19:40.096
- Well. there's been a lot of push back

420
00:19:40.137 --> 00:19:43.933
in terms of. you know. making me consider

421
00:19:43.974 --> 00:19:45.518
how much more fortunate I am

422
00:19:45.559 --> 00:19:47.645
than a lot of other people in the world.

423
00:19:47.687 --> 00:19:49.105
- [Ali] Yeah. I mean.
I guess I can get why.

424
00:19:49.146 --> 00:19:51.649
if you just. you know. say
it's like a personal journey.

425
00:19:51.691 --> 00:19:52.650
"This is the journey I'm on."

426
00:19:52.692 --> 00:19:54.944
those kind of sound like
buzzwords to people. you know?

427
00:19:54.985 --> 00:19:56.070
- [Liam] I think I need
to find a better way

428
00:19:56.112 --> 00:19:58.614
to articulate why it's important to me.

429
00:19:59.573 --> 00:20:00.991
because it is sincere.

430
00:20:01.033 --> 00:20:03.202
And I think that if I go out there and say.

431
00:20:03.244 --> 00:20:05.204
"Hey. I'm looking for a blessing."

432
00:20:05.246 --> 00:20:06.997
and I walk down the street

433
00:20:07.039 --> 00:20:09.125
and I find a $10 note.

434
00:20:09.208 --> 00:20:11.836
I feel like that won't change my mind.

435
00:20:11.877 --> 00:20:14.296
it won't be the validation
that I'm looking for.

436
00:20:14.338 --> 00:20:15.464
- [Ali] Are you nervous at all

437
00:20:15.506 --> 00:20:17.717
that if you do find someone
who's willing to curse you.

438
00:20:17.758 --> 00:20:19.802
like what that will actually be like?

439
00:20:20.177 --> 00:20:22.138
- [Liam] You know. I
don't know what to believe

440
00:20:22.179 --> 00:20:24.723
about any of this stuff anymore.

441
00:20:24.765 --> 00:20:26.767
I think at the beginning of this.

442
00:20:26.809 --> 00:20:31.147
maybe I was more skeptical
as the days have gone on.

443
00:20:32.189 --> 00:20:33.691
I'm not sure what I think anymore.

444
00:20:33.732 --> 00:20:36.485
(dramatic music)

445
00:20:39.655 --> 00:20:43.576
Should I really be
concerned about being cursed.

446
00:20:43.617 --> 00:20:45.786
and is there any actual evidence

447
00:20:45.828 --> 00:20:47.913
that magic could real?

448
00:20:49.165 --> 00:20:52.293
Thankfully. there are those
who are studying the science

449
00:20:52.334 --> 00:20:54.128
of this phenomena.

450
00:20:54.170 --> 00:20:58.048
Founded 50 years ago
by Apollo 14 astronaut.

451
00:20:58.090 --> 00:21:01.844
Dr. Edgar Mitchell. the
Institute of Noetic Sciences

452
00:21:01.886 --> 00:21:05.014
is one of the leading
centers for the investigation

453
00:21:05.055 --> 00:21:08.559
into the power of human consciousness.

454
00:21:08.601 --> 00:21:12.313
{\an8}- What we study are
exceptional experiences.

455
00:21:12.354 --> 00:21:14.023
{\an8}that's our euphemism.

456
00:21:14.064 --> 00:21:17.860
{\an8}But that means mystical
experience. psychic experience.

457
00:21:17.902 --> 00:21:20.779
and other kinds of
transformative experiences.

458
00:21:20.821 --> 00:21:24.909
- What are the goals of the
Institute of Noetic Sciences?

459
00:21:25.326 --> 00:21:28.120
- We have a working hypothesis

460
00:21:28.162 --> 00:21:31.040
that all minds are interconnected.

461
00:21:31.081 --> 00:21:34.251
And so part of the goal is to test ideas

462
00:21:34.293 --> 00:21:37.963
that would either confirm
or deny that hypothesis.

463
00:21:38.088 --> 00:21:40.841
Mostly we end up confirming it.

464
00:21:40.883 --> 00:21:43.636
And of course. this is part
of the esoteric traditions

465
00:21:43.677 --> 00:21:46.847
that go back as far as humanity goes.

466
00:21:46.889 --> 00:21:50.601
And we're trying to
apply the tools of science

467
00:21:50.643 --> 00:21:53.020
to better understand what apparently

468
00:21:53.062 --> 00:21:55.314
the ancients knew quite well.

469
00:21:55.356 --> 00:21:57.233
- So I'm particularly interested

470
00:21:57.274 --> 00:22:00.402
in the idea of force of will. magic.

471
00:22:00.444 --> 00:22:03.072
and does thought intention

472
00:22:03.113 --> 00:22:05.074
really affect the world around us?

473
00:22:05.115 --> 00:22:06.951
- So in the laboratory.

474
00:22:06.992 --> 00:22:09.995
that kind of experiment is looking is thought about

475
00:22:10.037 --> 00:22:13.165
as a mind matter interaction.

476
00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:16.669
Does the mind. is the mind able to change something

477
00:22:16.710 --> 00:22:19.046
that is physically
measurable at a distance?

478
00:22:20.172 --> 00:22:22.091
Well. the answer is yes.

479
00:22:22.132 --> 00:22:26.345
Of the largest single class of studies

480
00:22:26.428 --> 00:22:29.265
involve random physical systems.

481
00:22:29.306 --> 00:22:31.809
We're talking about electronic
random number generators.

482
00:22:31.851 --> 00:22:35.437
So you ask somebody while
the bits are being created.

483
00:22:35.479 --> 00:22:38.857
that simply will more ones to come up

484
00:22:38.899 --> 00:22:40.192
or more zeroes to come up.

485
00:22:40.234 --> 00:22:44.363
And so after 50 or more
years of doing experiments

486
00:22:44.405 --> 00:22:48.284
as part of a laboratory test. that works.

487
00:22:48.325 --> 00:22:49.326
So we take all of that

488
00:22:49.368 --> 00:22:51.161
and we then are address the question of.

489
00:22:51.203 --> 00:22:52.705
"Well. does force of will work?"

490
00:22:52.788 --> 00:22:53.873
In the real world.

491
00:22:53.914 --> 00:22:56.542
I would say the affirmations. magic spells.

492
00:22:56.584 --> 00:22:58.294
and all the rest. they do work.

493
00:22:59.169 --> 00:23:00.754
but usually they don't work

494
00:23:00.796 --> 00:23:03.966
at anywhere near the same speed

495
00:23:04.008 --> 00:23:05.843
as what we see in the laboratory.

496
00:23:06.802 --> 00:23:09.013
- [Liam] Traditional
witchcraft practitioners

497
00:23:09.054 --> 00:23:10.890
believe their spell crafting

498
00:23:10.931 --> 00:23:13.934
can affect the world around us.

499
00:23:13.976 --> 00:23:16.520
And now scientists are finding evidence

500
00:23:16.562 --> 00:23:21.525
that the human mind can
affect digital systems in the lab.

501
00:23:21.567 --> 00:23:24.236
One of the largest
experiments on the subject

502
00:23:24.278 --> 00:23:27.615
was conducted by the
Global Consciousness Project.

503
00:23:27.656 --> 00:23:30.284
The group placed random number generators

504
00:23:30.326 --> 00:23:32.536
around densely populated cities

505
00:23:32.578 --> 00:23:34.580
to see if the thoughts and emotions

506
00:23:34.622 --> 00:23:36.248
of large groups of people

507
00:23:36.290 --> 00:23:38.334
could skew the machine's readings

508
00:23:38.375 --> 00:23:42.922
away from a 50-50 chance
of being a one or a zero.

509
00:23:42.963 --> 00:23:45.591
especially during major world events.

510
00:23:45.633 --> 00:23:48.886
(tense dramatic music)

511
00:23:52.640 --> 00:23:55.059
The data recorded on these machines

512
00:23:55.100 --> 00:23:57.353
around the events of September 11th

513
00:23:57.394 --> 00:24:00.648
showed significant
deviations that for many.

514
00:24:00.689 --> 00:24:05.611
suggest evidence of a unified
field of human consciousness.

515
00:24:06.487 --> 00:24:08.989
I've asked magical practitioners

516
00:24:09.031 --> 00:24:12.534
if they would. in some way.
give me a negative spell.

517
00:24:12.576 --> 00:24:15.204
or that would could be a curse or a hex.

