780
00:36:23.932 --> 00:36:26.267
And those are very interesting topics.

781
00:36:26.309 --> 00:36:28.478
not what we study in parapsychology.

782
00:36:28.520 --> 00:36:30.438
Parapsychology is actually a science

783
00:36:30.480 --> 00:36:33.316
that studies five very specific phenomenon.

784
00:36:33.358 --> 00:36:37.362
{\an8}One being telepathy. mind
to mind communication.

785
00:36:37.404 --> 00:36:40.073
{\an8}another. clairvoyance. getting information

786
00:36:40.115 --> 00:36:42.992
{\an8}about objects or events that are hidden.

787
00:36:43.118 --> 00:36:45.245
{\an8}Third area is precognition.

788
00:36:45.286 --> 00:36:47.747
{\an8}getting information through time.

789
00:36:47.789 --> 00:36:50.125
We group them together and call them ESP

790
00:36:50.166 --> 00:36:52.836
or extra sensory perception.

791
00:36:52.877 --> 00:36:54.379
In addition to ESP.

792
00:36:54.421 --> 00:36:56.923
{\an8}we also study psychokinesis.

793
00:36:56.965 --> 00:36:59.259
{\an8}mind matter interaction.

794
00:36:59.300 --> 00:37:02.053
{\an8}The fifth area is survival studies.

795
00:37:02.095 --> 00:37:04.139
{\an8}Survival studies includes everything

796
00:37:04.180 --> 00:37:06.266
from near death experiences.

797
00:37:06.307 --> 00:37:07.475
out of body experiences.

798
00:37:07.517 --> 00:37:09.602
past lives or reincarnation.

799
00:37:09.644 --> 00:37:10.854
So those are the five areas

800
00:37:10.895 --> 00:37:12.188
that parapsychologists study.

