1117
00:57:49.091 --> 00:57:51.385
I had a big climbing accident.

1118
00:57:51.426 --> 00:57:54.221
- Yeah. I know you told
me about that before.

1119
00:57:54.262 --> 00:57:59.226
- So I was climbing a big
route back home in the UK.

1120
00:57:59.267 --> 00:58:00.227
I got right to the top.

1121
00:58:00.268 --> 00:58:02.980
