out of the rock that was stuck.

1128
00:58:19.121 --> 00:58:20.414
And the minute my foot came out.

1129
00:58:20.455 --> 00:58:24.042
my hands came away. and I fell.

1130
00:58:24.084 --> 00:58:27.087
I just remember putting
my hands over my eyes.

1131
00:58:27.129 --> 00:58:29.297
I just remember thinking. "I'm gonna die.

1132
00:58:30.257 --> 00:58:33.260
I just don't want to
see it when it happens."

1133
00:58:33.301 --> 00:58:35.595
This is where it gets strange.

1134
00:58:35.637 --> 00:58:40.434
I went from the most
fear I've ever had in my life

1135
00:58:42.269 --> 00:58:46.148
to feeling an in incredible.

1136
00:58:46.189 --> 00:58:50.027
incredible sense of bliss.

1137
00:58:50.068 --> 00:58:55.031
I felt so at peace

1138
00:58:55.073 --> 00:58:56.950
in a way that was just incredible.

1139
00:58:56.992 --> 00:59:01.955
Just to this day. it makes no sense.

1140
00:59:01.997 --> 00:59:05.667
By luck. I didn't hit the
ground. and I was like.

1141
00:59:05.792 --> 00:59:07.961
"I'm alive." (chuckles)

1142
00:59:08.003 --> 00:59:10.255
I felt like I touched something

1143
00:59:10.297 --> 00:59:15.719
