1153
00:59:39.076 --> 00:59:40.452
And I think that's what I'm looking for.

1154
00:59:40.494 --> 00:59:43.747
(eerie dramatic music)

1155
00:59:49.252 --> 00:59:52.005
(dramatic music)

1156
