whether magical or psychological.

1255
01:11:14.145 --> 01:11:15.730
I guess I'll have to wait and see.

1256
01:11:15.772 --> 01:11:19.025
(tense dramatic music)

1257
01:11:26.991 --> 01:11:31.996
