1278
01:14:59.453 --> 01:15:01.997
We know that science has proved things

1279
01:15:02.039 --> 01:15:04.667
like the placebo and nocebo effect.

1280
01:15:04.709 --> 01:15:08.045
and our minds can have physical effects

1281
01:15:08.087 --> 01:15:10.798
on our bodies when we believe.

1282
01:15:11.924 --> 01:15:13.801
My feelings about regret might be different

1283
01:15:13.843 --> 01:15:17.138
if I was to find out
that my medical results

1284
01:15:17.179 --> 01:15:19.640
show up a problem that I
didn't have six months ago.

1285
01:15:19.807 --> 01:15:21.892
(dramatic music)

1286
01:15:27.732 --> 01:15:29.650
So mountain biking is definitely one

1287
01:15:29.692 --> 01:15:31.777
of my biggest passions in life.

1288
01:15:31.819 --> 01:15:35.531
There really is nothing
like getting down the trails.

1289
01:15:35.573 --> 01:15:37.700
shredding. having fun.

1290
01:15:37.742 --> 01:15:40.536
And I gotta admit. since
going to New Orleans.

1291
01:15:40.578 --> 01:15:41.996
getting a curse.

1292
01:15:42.037 --> 01:15:45.207
and then coming outta the cave in Mexico.

1293
01:15:45.249 --> 01:15:48.127
it's put me off riding and
that's been getting me down.

1294
01:15:48.169 --> 01:15:51.714
So I've decided to put
that behind me right now.

1295
01:15:51.756 --> 01:15:54.175
I gotta get out on the
trails. have some fun.

1296
01:15:54.216 --> 01:15:57.219
and just stop thinking
about all that stuff. you know?

1297
01:15:57.261 --> 01:16:00.014
(dramatic music)

1298
01:16:14.111 --> 01:16:17.656
(dramatic music continues)

1299
01:16:27.249 --> 01:16:32.254
(chains rattling) (Liam grunting)

1300
01:16:32.463 --> 01:16:33.380
- [Rider] Dude. are you okay?

1301
01:16:33.422 --> 01:16:35.591
- Ah. my knee. argh...

1302
01:16:38.052 --> 01:16:39.053
- Yeah...

1303
01:16:39.470 --> 01:16:43.474
The hospital X-ray showed
nothing was broken. thankfully.

1304
01:16:43.516 --> 01:16:46.602
but I had a pretty deep
cut that needed stitches.

1305
01:16:46.644 --> 01:16:49.522
The swelling to the
knee was pretty extensive

1306
01:16:49.563 --> 01:16:50.981
and took five or six weeks

1307
01:16:51.023 --> 01:16:54.151
to try and get myself
walking properly again.

1308
01:16:54.235 --> 01:16:56.195
Even when I tried to get away from it.

1309
01:16:56.278 --> 01:16:58.656
my mind's haunted by curses.

1310
01:16:59.824 --> 01:17:03.369
Where your attention
goes. your energy flows.

1311
01:17:03.410 --> 01:17:07.081
and I fear I'm becoming a danger to myself.

1312
01:17:08.082 --> 01:17:10.626
(tense dramatic music)

1313
01:17:10.668 --> 01:17:14.672
(Liam grunting) (tense dramatic music)

1314
01:17:14.755 --> 01:17:17.842
What is strange though is
I checked out the footage

1315
01:17:17.883 --> 01:17:22.888
from Elias' curse and where
he got specific shocked me.

1316
01:17:23.389 --> 01:17:25.933
- The Lord shall smite thee in the knees

1317
01:17:25.975 --> 01:17:28.727
and in the legs. (laughs)

1318
01:17:30.771 --> 01:17:32.022
- [Liam] Is magic real.

1319
01:17:32.064 --> 01:17:34.024
and if so. where does it come from?

1320
01:17:34.817 --> 01:17:37.194
{\an8}- Magic is the fact

1321
01:17:37.236 --> 01:17:41.740
{\an8}that you are an animate
creature existing currently

1322
01:17:41.907 --> 01:17:44.285
who is conscious enough
to ask the question.

1323
01:17:44.326 --> 01:17:45.703
That is magic.

1324
01:17:45.744 --> 01:17:49.415
So yes. magic is real as that.

1325
01:17:49.456 --> 01:17:52.042
It's not wrong to go
out and seek experiences.

1326
01:17:52.084 --> 01:17:53.419
There is value in it.

1327
01:17:53.460 --> 01:17:58.090
but you have to. you have to. be careful

1328
01:17:58.132 --> 01:18:00.801
'cause all those things. all those things are true.

1329
01:18:01.093 --> 01:18:02.595
all those things are very. very true.

1330
01:18:02.636 --> 01:18:05.890
(eerie dramatic music)

1331
01:18:09.101 --> 01:18:10.936
- It is been several months now

1332
01:18:11.020 --> 01:18:13.355
and the dreams are just getting worse.

1333
01:18:13.397 --> 01:18:15.941
I'm barely sleeping at the moment.

1334
01:18:15.983 --> 01:18:18.736
and the sense of anxiety
that I wake up with

1335
01:18:18.777 --> 01:18:21.864
carries on with me throughout the day.

1336
01:18:21.906 --> 01:18:24.200
I feel paranoid all the time.

1337
01:18:24.241 --> 01:18:25.367
Even sitting in traffic.

1338
01:18:25.409 --> 01:18:29.079
I keep thinking that
every car's going to hit me.

1339
01:18:29.121 --> 01:18:30.456
Every time the phone rings.

1340
01:18:30.497 --> 01:18:33.167
I think that something bad has happened.

1341
01:18:33.209 --> 01:18:36.545
and it's just this constant sense of dread.

1342
01:18:36.587 --> 01:18:39.340
(dramatic music)

1343
01:18:41.508 --> 01:18:44.178
Maybe it's connected to my lack of sleep.

1344
01:18:44.219 --> 01:18:47.640
but I have this physical feeling

1345
01:18:47.681 --> 01:18:49.391
that something bad is coming.

1346
01:18:49.433 --> 01:18:52.686
(tense dramatic music)

1347
01:19:01.153 --> 01:19:03.948
- How long do you wanna
remain the cursed man?

1348
01:19:04.907 --> 01:19:07.076
- I think I've had enough.

1349
01:19:07.117 --> 01:19:10.955
- Was it the dreams where you
said I've had enough. exactly?

1350
01:19:10.996 --> 01:19:14.875
Or was it the accident or the anxiety?

1351
01:19:14.917 --> 01:19:15.960
- As the odd little things

1352
01:19:16.001 --> 01:19:18.128
that are more physical are happening.

1353
01:19:18.170 --> 01:19:22.383
it's chipping away at the
armor of it's all in your mind.

1354
01:19:22.424 --> 01:19:25.928
And I feel like if I don't try

1355
01:19:25.970 --> 01:19:28.055
and maybe undo this some way.

1356
01:19:28.097 --> 01:19:30.432
whether or not magic is real or not.

1357
01:19:31.308 --> 01:19:35.521
I might be finding and forming
some real negative habits.

1358
01:19:35.562 --> 01:19:37.982
- So what has stopped you so far

1359
01:19:38.107 --> 01:19:42.361
from releasing yourself from them?

1360
01:19:42.403 --> 01:19:43.737
- I don't know whether or not it's gonna be

1361
01:19:43.779 --> 01:19:46.782
as easy to do as just that.

1362
01:19:46.824 --> 01:19:48.742
I think now I'm in a tricky position

1363
01:19:48.826 --> 01:19:51.996
where if I perhaps

1364
01:19:52.997 --> 01:19:55.582
didn't believe in magic.

1365
01:19:55.624 --> 01:19:58.961
and yet somehow it's
got into my subconscious

1366
01:19:59.003 --> 01:20:01.964
that now I'm actually
going to have to believe

1367
01:20:02.006 --> 01:20:04.008
in order to get myself out of this.

1368
01:20:06.969 --> 01:20:09.638
{\an8}(siren wailing)

1369
01:20:11.640 --> 01:20:13.684
Despite your warnings-

1370
01:20:13.726 --> 01:20:18.022
- Yes?
- I have found not one.

1371
01:20:18.063 --> 01:20:23.068
{\an8}but two people who were
prepared to put a curse on me.

1372
01:20:23.402 --> 01:20:25.237
{\an8}- See. this is why they
wonder of us as Brits.

1373
01:20:25.279 --> 01:20:28.240
{\an8}they think we're crazy.
- Right. but I can't imagine why.

1374
01:20:29.408 --> 01:20:32.411
{\an8}- And I feel like I'm getting
a laundry list of things

1375
01:20:32.453 --> 01:20:34.330
that are starting to go wrong.

1376
01:20:34.371 --> 01:20:37.499
I have brought with me a couple of clips

1377
01:20:37.541 --> 01:20:39.960
from the things that have been done to me.

1378
01:20:41.211 --> 01:20:43.005
- We're going to be first tying you

1379
01:20:43.047 --> 01:20:46.508
to one of these coffin nails.

1380
01:20:46.550 --> 01:20:48.886
So some of your hair.
the Lord shall smite thee

1381
01:20:48.927 --> 01:20:51.096
with a consumption and with a fever.

1382
01:20:51.263 --> 01:20:53.891
and with an inflammation
and with an extreme burning.

1383
01:20:53.932 --> 01:20:56.727
and they shall pursue
thee until thy perish.

1384
01:20:56.769 --> 01:20:59.313
The Lord shall smite thee in the knees
- God...

1385
01:20:59.354 --> 01:21:02.066
and in the legs. (laughs)

1386
01:21:03.984 --> 01:21:06.779
And he shall put forth a
yoke of iron upon thy neck

1387
01:21:07.738 --> 01:21:09.823
until he had destroyed thee.

1388
01:21:09.865 --> 01:21:11.158
- Wow.

1389
01:21:11.200 --> 01:21:12.785
- Damn dude! (chuckles)

1390
01:21:12.826 --> 01:21:14.328
- So that was about six months ago now.

1391
01:21:14.370 --> 01:21:16.580
and there's certainly been
some things happening to me.

1392
01:21:16.622 --> 01:21:18.332
- Did it start happening in your dreams?

1393
01:21:18.374 --> 01:21:20.751
- Yes. now I'm having pretty severe

1394
01:21:20.793 --> 01:21:22.086
nightmares now actually.

1395
01:21:22.127 --> 01:21:23.045
- You haven't lost any limbs

1396
01:21:23.087 --> 01:21:25.297
or anything since though. right? (laughs)

1397
01:21:25.339 --> 01:21:29.885
- No. about five. six weeks after

1398
01:21:29.927 --> 01:21:32.805
that happened to my knee.

1399
01:21:32.888 --> 01:21:35.766
I had to have stitches in the knee.
- Okay.

1400
01:21:35.808 --> 01:21:36.600
- That's nasty.

1401
01:21:36.642 --> 01:21:38.936
- It doesn't stop with the
knee though. it goes on.

1402
01:21:39.228 --> 01:21:40.437
- If you don't cut this short.

1403
01:21:40.479 --> 01:21:41.647
this can get really bad...
- It's gonna start

1404
01:21:41.688 --> 01:21:43.273
to get very physical.
- Yeah.

1405
01:21:43.315 --> 01:21:44.858
- Perhaps I should have stopped there.

1406
01:21:44.900 --> 01:21:47.694
I found a brujo in Mexico

1407
01:21:47.736 --> 01:21:51.573
who aligns his work
specifically with Satan.

1408
01:21:51.657 --> 01:21:54.743
He told me that I had
to write down the request

1409
01:21:54.785 --> 01:21:56.829
and I would petition that request to Satan

1410
01:21:56.870 --> 01:21:58.580
at a very special place.

1411
01:21:58.747 --> 01:22:01.333
I did that. and it was bound in blood.

1412
01:22:01.375 --> 01:22:03.836
- Binding with blood
doesn't make it easy to undo.

1413
01:22:03.877 --> 01:22:06.421
(tense dramatic music)

1414
01:22:14.596 --> 01:22:17.057
- Satan. this is my request to you.

1415
01:22:17.099 --> 01:22:20.602
and I humbly offer it to
you. and I thank you for it.

1416
01:22:29.111 --> 01:22:30.070
- Oh he marked you.

1417
01:22:33.240 --> 01:22:37.035
This one is something that
you got marked and you got.

1418
01:22:37.077 --> 01:22:39.496
and you petitioned. so...

1419
01:22:39.538 --> 01:22:41.415
- For a life. not just the curse.

1420
01:22:41.456 --> 01:22:43.167
but this is gonna be your life from now on.

1421
01:22:43.208 --> 01:22:44.626
was basically what I was hearing.

1422
01:22:44.668 --> 01:22:46.503
- Problem here is you're approaching it

1423
01:22:46.545 --> 01:22:47.546
like a party trick.

1424
01:22:47.588 --> 01:22:50.841
and so therefore that
very action is disrespectful.

1425
01:22:50.883 --> 01:22:53.635
And for that. you may get. you may get a slap.

1426
01:22:53.677 --> 01:22:56.138
or we may have a fight on our hands.

1427
01:22:56.180 --> 01:22:57.723
To be honest. just so you know.

1428
01:22:57.764 --> 01:22:59.641
going into trying to undo this.

1429
01:22:59.683 --> 01:23:01.852
you are gonna have to find faith in this

1430
01:23:01.894 --> 01:23:03.061
in order to undo it.

1431
01:23:03.145 --> 01:23:06.023
You're gonna be the key to undoing it.

1432
01:23:06.064 --> 01:23:09.234
- Okay. (dramatic music)

1433
01:23:19.953 --> 01:23:23.457
(dramatic music continues)

1434
01:23:33.342 --> 01:23:34.509
- Okay. you ready?

1435
01:23:34.593 --> 01:23:37.054
- I am.
- All right. come with me.

1436
01:23:40.390 --> 01:23:45.395
- One is thine. three for thee.

1437
01:23:46.772 --> 01:23:51.693
nine is mine. (dramatic music)

1438
01:23:54.363 --> 01:23:58.200
One for the land and one for you.

1439
01:23:59.326 --> 01:24:00.494
One for thine.

1440
01:24:01.870 --> 01:24:06.375
three for thee. and nine is mine.

1441
01:24:06.500 --> 01:24:07.876
Psychic protection.

1442
01:24:07.918 --> 01:24:09.253
- And as each person comes in.

1443
01:24:09.294 --> 01:24:13.006
you are going to give them one coin each.

1444
01:24:13.048 --> 01:24:17.886
Three for thee. and nine is mine.

1445
01:24:17.970 --> 01:24:20.722
(dramatic music)

1446
01:24:23.141 --> 01:24:24.643
Accept your payment.

1447
01:24:24.685 --> 01:24:27.437
(dramatic music)

1448
01:24:31.358 --> 01:24:35.404
Nine is mine. (dramatic music)

1449
01:24:37.072 --> 01:24:39.408
- I accept your payment for this work.

1450
01:24:39.449 --> 01:24:42.202
(dramatic music)

1451
01:24:46.331 --> 01:24:51.128
We are grouped here
together to close contracts

1452
01:24:51.169 --> 01:24:53.422
for Liam. legitimate reasons.

1453
01:24:53.463 --> 01:24:55.048
I think he was a fool.

1454
01:24:55.090 --> 01:24:56.675
but we are here to undo it.

1455
01:24:56.717 --> 01:24:59.970
(tense dramatic music)

1456
01:25:02.055 --> 01:25:06.518
I call upon my gods. Croman.

1457
01:25:07.352 --> 01:25:09.396
hear the blood in my veins

1458
01:25:09.438 --> 01:25:12.190
know the oaths I have
made on the ancient altars.

1459
01:25:13.191 --> 01:25:15.986
I call to the watchers.

1460
01:25:16.028 --> 01:25:18.739
black spirits and white.
red spirits and gray.

1461
01:25:18.780 --> 01:25:21.158
mingle. mingle. mingle. who may.

1462
01:25:21.241 --> 01:25:23.493
felt out. out. out around and about.

1463
01:25:23.535 --> 01:25:28.749
a world within and a world without.

1464
01:25:28.790 --> 01:25:32.878
the good. stay in. and the ill. stay out.

1465
01:25:32.961 --> 01:25:35.714
(dramatic music)

1466
01:25:37.841 --> 01:25:40.886
- Two curses have been placed upon Liam.

1467
01:25:42.012 --> 01:25:45.432
The first was made to be undone.

1468
01:25:46.933 --> 01:25:49.144
In the service of Liam.

1469
01:25:49.186 --> 01:25:50.771
I now in this moment.

1470
01:25:50.812 --> 01:25:53.357
(sickle clattering)

1471
01:25:53.398 --> 01:25:58.195
sever. this curse. hmm bound tight.

1472
01:25:58.236 --> 01:26:00.947
(dramatic music)

1473
01:26:09.456 --> 01:26:12.084
Unravel and clean.

1474
01:26:12.125 --> 01:26:14.211
Take it apart. shred it.

1475
01:26:14.252 --> 01:26:16.254
get it all broken up.

1476
01:26:16.296 --> 01:26:18.090
Here. take the sickle. cut some threads.

1477
01:26:18.131 --> 01:26:21.927
cut the fabric. get it removed. severed.

1478
01:26:23.720 --> 01:26:26.348
give blessings to the one that served you.

1479
01:26:27.432 --> 01:26:29.810
Know that it has done its job.

1480
01:26:29.851 --> 01:26:33.105
(tense dramatic music)

1481
01:26:34.606 --> 01:26:36.817
- Thank you for giving me this experience.

1482
01:26:36.858 --> 01:26:38.318
But I'm glad that it's ended.

1483
01:26:38.360 --> 01:26:40.487
This is over and it is done.

1484
01:26:40.612 --> 01:26:43.698
(tense dramatic music)

1485
01:26:47.452 --> 01:26:48.662
- The next one is harder.

1486
01:26:48.704 --> 01:26:51.248
(wand rattling)

1487
01:26:51.373 --> 01:26:52.290
Coven tread.

1488
01:26:52.332 --> 01:26:54.209
(wand rattling)

1489
01:26:54.251 --> 01:26:58.922
(ritualists pagan chanting)

1490
01:27:07.347 --> 01:27:09.641
- I call to you fallen angel.

1491
01:27:10.559 --> 01:27:14.896
the contract now he
asks be brought to close.

1492
01:27:15.897 --> 01:27:17.774
the knowledge he has gleaned

1493
01:27:17.858 --> 01:27:20.360
he knows to be true.

1494
01:27:20.402 --> 01:27:22.863
and through this work that he is doing.

1495
01:27:22.904 --> 01:27:26.074
he will share this
knowledge with the world.

1496
01:27:26.116 --> 01:27:30.078
For this. he asks that
recognition of this pact

1497
01:27:30.120 --> 01:27:33.582
be completed and laid down.

1498
01:27:33.623 --> 01:27:34.875
Look into the mirror

1499
01:27:34.916 --> 01:27:37.043
and speak to that completion.

1500
01:27:38.253 --> 01:27:40.422
Do you know it to be true. Liam?

1501
01:27:40.464 --> 01:27:42.758
- Yes. I know this to be true.

1502
01:27:42.799 --> 01:27:44.801
I recognize the power.

1503
01:27:44.843 --> 01:27:46.470
I have had enough.

1504
01:27:46.511 --> 01:27:47.596
- You are ready.

1505
01:27:47.637 --> 01:27:48.597
- I am ready.

1506
01:27:48.638 --> 01:27:51.183
This is completely over. it is done.

1507
01:27:51.224 --> 01:27:53.143
I am finished with this.

1508
01:27:53.185 --> 01:27:56.772
- Do you see that day
that you were in that cave

1509
01:27:56.813 --> 01:27:58.273
and you made this pact?

1510
01:27:58.315 --> 01:27:59.191
- Yes.

1511
01:27:59.232 --> 01:28:03.695
- Push. push. you feel the pact?

1512
01:28:03.862 --> 01:28:04.863
- Yes. I feel it.

1513
01:28:04.946 --> 01:28:06.156
- You see him before you.

1514
01:28:06.198 --> 01:28:08.283
- I can see him. yeah. I felt that energy.

1515
01:28:08.325 --> 01:28:09.451
- Do you feel it now?

1516
01:28:09.534 --> 01:28:10.368
- I can feel it. yes.

1517
01:28:10.410 --> 01:28:12.245
- Now. sever them tethers.

1518
01:28:12.287 --> 01:28:13.538
Sever them. one by one.

1519
01:28:13.580 --> 01:28:15.040
Rip them to shreds.

1520
01:28:15.081 --> 01:28:16.625
- I have severed these tethers.

1521
01:28:16.666 --> 01:28:18.251
I've severed these bindings.

1522
01:28:18.293 --> 01:28:21.213
- With honor and respect.

1523
01:28:21.254 --> 01:28:22.923
- Feel it all that is bound in you

1524
01:28:22.964 --> 01:28:25.217
now be bound within that mirror.

1525
01:28:25.550 --> 01:28:26.426
- Use your breath.

1526
01:28:26.718 --> 01:28:28.595
(Liam breathes deeply)

1527
01:28:28.678 --> 01:28:29.471
- Again.

1528
01:28:29.721 --> 01:28:31.681
- Roar. roar. (Liam roaring)

1529
01:28:31.765 --> 01:28:36.144
- Roar! (Liam roaring)

1530
01:28:36.311 --> 01:28:38.063
- Yes.
- Come on. push.

